  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-39eea311-1311-4805-a8f7-2c6f51fb8121\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-39eea311-1311-4805-a8f7-2c6f51fb8121\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAzMjdfODAg/MDAxNzQzMDczMTc2MDA5.F-ObqTt-_gqdeQwtO3PJC54PtsmVsjLErO8J2OS1ylwg.0wmg32DvtyKVxNUKKrk29FwtOOtPUYjQDDYa4Bo2Tx8g.PNG/1.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1418\", \"originalHeight\" : \"2954\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAzMjdfODAg/MDAxNzQzMDczMTc2MDA5.F-ObqTt-_gqdeQwtO3PJC54PtsmVsjLErO8J2OS1ylwg.0wmg32DvtyKVxNUKKrk29FwtOOtPUYjQDDYa4Bo2Tx8g.PNG/1.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\" id=\"SE-6f75af02-6ff3-435f-8eba-bbb0ccb9e28f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_underline\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-2c5c4a63-a216-4ecc-b125-98a41cc08783\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-a81f120a-8635-45e4-86d3-e9e2787e0be1\" style=\"\">제작 의도</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-f62fbc9d-5716-4df3-92f3-7730ff840812\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f6c3d687-bb66-450f-a92f-7f6a5d12ba8e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-1605ee7f-8c6b-4f8f-a16d-a8648e94dcb2\" style=\"color:#555555;\">가끔 신규 고객이 문의를 해오면 그분의 카카오톡 프로필 사진을 보곤 합니다. 염탐은 아니고 그분의 미력한 정보를 조금이라도 얻고자 함입니다. 이럴 때 개인정보도 있겠지만 노출을 꺼리는 사람들이고 회사 폰이라면 프로필 사진을 거의 무 배경으로 저장해 놓곤 합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-2a9b4730-9320-4b33-af1b-a96837d117bb\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:648px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-2a9b4730-9320-4b33-af1b-a96837d117bb\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAzMjdfMTUx/MDAxNzQzMDcyODM3NzE2.pF1b_wBYIjuRPlAQYARBJhrRvX0_6LjGRJkWyJHLDiYg.tiiVmGRvuO2VL7OJp4XVBDx9n6EVxoVfLbyMQ9rt3Lgg.JPEG/SE-2a9b4730-9320-4b33-af1b-a96837d117bb.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"648\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1390\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAzMjdfMTUx/MDAxNzQzMDcyODM3NzE2.pF1b_wBYIjuRPlAQYARBJhrRvX0_6LjGRJkWyJHLDiYg.tiiVmGRvuO2VL7OJp4XVBDx9n6EVxoVfLbyMQ9rt3Lgg.JPEG/SE-2a9b4730-9320-4b33-af1b-a96837d117bb.jpg?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-5410e222-0394-416a-98c2-8146aedddea1\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4cbe1dfb-2e79-48a5-8961-36fc446fb6e2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-84aea929-b9d1-4422-8bc1-514430cfa4b8\" style=\"color:#555555;\">하지만 단 1초 단 1페이지라도 자신을 홍보하고 싶은 영업맨이시라면 법인폰의 프로필을 자신의 영업 이미지로 바꿔보시는 건 어떻까요?</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-65bf94f9-b1e9-4611-8607-c963598599c5\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:648px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-65bf94f9-b1e9-4611-8607-c963598599c5\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAzMjdfMTYz/MDAxNzQzMDczNzI1NzUy.daxOGU045ZlyiCSUUDl2Y0PnYYOpST0FvtBHNyQ7B5Mg.AQpiMq0HHTYc6nKGHg88xidhCaDNtwd30US4LRQfMkwg.JPEG/SE-65bf94f9-b1e9-4611-8607-c963598599c5.jpg\", \"originalWidth\" : \"648\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1390\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyNTAzMjdfMTYz/MDAxNzQzMDczNzI1NzUy.daxOGU045ZlyiCSUUDl2Y0PnYYOpST0FvtBHNyQ7B5Mg.AQpiMq0HHTYc6nKGHg88xidhCaDNtwd30US4LRQfMkwg.JPEG/SE-65bf94f9-b1e9-4611-8607-c963598599c5.jpg?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-9991ae05-74f1-44a1-9e4e-21c13ff450c8\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-464e7f90-2144-4907-be4f-5f12f408df0a\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b8238262-e2f4-46f7-8b37-1d2e21995326\" style=\"color:#555555;\">당신이 만약 영업사원이고 자신의 홍보가 목숨과 같은 위치에 계시다면 프로필도 이미지로 만들어서 사람들에게 어필해 보시기 바랍니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-b4aa0305-01c3-4038-abdd-5a6b27233b44\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-fa98fba3-fda0-4ff2-a9a6-2536279f55dd\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-4d46dec7-b693-4c4c-8e57-f95680e55a57\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-e324ecf9-001b-4e3b-ac98-b0319277cd0b\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-90f33a1a-7317-421e-aaa1-8769c8998762\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-8f9a908e-46bd-4043-adde-b72c05f44a04\" style=\"color:#007aa6;\"><b>이런 분께 추천드립니다.</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-1a78423d-7d86-4d4c-a149-80caa989fb18\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-5721e94d-bd0d-47b8-89da-35cac3d80fb9\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-7264fccb-b1a3-495f-9c66-ec0332948f88\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-4a8ccfc3-461f-4fa1-8790-4c729f900b5e\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>영업이 주업인 업종</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c4d1bb80-1316-48a8-be7d-6619bb515e40\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 보험설계사, 자동차 딜러, 부동산 중개 등</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-68612d1a-d38c-496e-9d99-172a86f5dc9b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-69242aed-c5f3-4234-846d-412d2e34777c\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>전문직 종사자</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-a0aa4110-b40e-4bfd-9964-f68a0a730555\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 변호사, 의사, 세무사, 변리사, 회계사 등 전문지에 종사하는 분</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-e95aed1b-cb7b-4e6a-85a3-e937acc5ba12\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-faa85bd0-38cf-4f68-85fb-eb3fd8a97557\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>개인 퍼스널브렌딩 종사</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-d0109352-45bb-4965-a9a6-f8defc111ee3\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 퍼스널 트레이너, 개인 코칭, 컨설턴트 등</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-0c990219-5525-401d-b508-68118bb6b6a7\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b2180d8e-b49c-4675-b635-e943c7df3d50\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>정치 및 종교인</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-b84ff3d1-dfee-4632-8652-8e9e6b3afd43\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 국회의원, 지방의회 의원, 목사, 수녀, 스님 등</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f7f267b3-2ef9-402c-8dfe-91248e9fab61\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-c87157e3-5e50-4630-8c92-2c1854c9923f\" style=\"color:#555555;\"><b>기타</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-2a2e80dc-6064-415f-b980-8db0792e0b17\" style=\"color:#555555;\"> : 헬스 트레이너, 예술인 등 개인의 프로필이 무기인 분</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-43337e7f-44f2-415a-be91-3f4d3934730d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-nanummaruburi\" id=\"SE-ddc623a2-68d6-4e7f-8665-584410ce9586\" style=\"color:#555555;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c46ac024-7ea6-41ef-bff3-e9a08dec1330\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-9c085ee5-f066-46bd-b2e5-150804da461f\" style=\"color:#555555;\">----------------------</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\